	(mate_canvas_group_set_property),
	(mate_canvas_group_get_property), (pick_current_item), (paint):
	Remove a bunch of crufty unused code and compiler warnings.

2005-12-21  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@ximian.com>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas.c (put_item_after): Simplify the
	code and make it correct - it wasn't resetting the item_list_end
	correctly when moving the last item in the list.  Fixes bug #323850.

2005-11-10  Simos Xenitellis  <simos@mate.org>

	* configure.in: Added Tatar (tt) to ALL_LINGUAS.

2005-11-06  Sven Herzberg  <herzi@mate-de.org>

	reviewed by: Tim Janik <timj@gtk.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas.c: added g_object_notify() to allow
	users to connect to the notify::parent signal, closes bug 320791

2005-10-06  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@ximian.com>

	Merged from the mate-2-12 branch:

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-pixbuf.c
	(mate_canvas_pixbuf_render): HYPER interpolation is a slow buggy piece of
	shit.  Use BILINEAR.  Fixes bug #129891.

2005-10-07  Danek Duvall <danek.duvall@sun.com>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas.h: Cast MATE_CANVAS_COLOR macros
	to use unsigned ints so that shifting left 24 bits won't overflow
	into the sign bit. Fixes #317718.

Thu Sep  8 10:56:26 2005  Tim Janik  <timj@gtk.org>

	* applied patch from hans de graaff with minor cosmetic fixups.

2005-07-15  Hans de Graaff  <hans@degraaff.org>

        * libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-pixbuf.c:
        (compute_viewport_affine): Multiply the width and height with the
        scaling factor when using middle or east anchors so that the new
        position is correctly calculated for width_in_pixels and
        height_in_pixels pixbufs.

========================= 2.12.0 ==========================

2005-09-06  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* configure.in: Release 2.12.0.

2005-08-29  Tor Lillqvist  <tml@novell.com>

	* libmatecanvas/Makefile.am: No need to install the Win32 import
	library separately, libtool --install does it.

	* libmatecanvas-zip.in: Include also documentation in the
	developer package.

	* tests/Makefile.am (TESTS_ENVIRONMENT): Fix Makefile variable
	syntax (add parens).

2005-06-07  Ignacio Casal Quinteiro  <nacho.resa@gmail.com>

	* configure.in: Added 'gl' to ALL_LINGUAS.

2005-05-24  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* Fix the fix for bug #90259 here too.

2005-05-19  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-text.c:
	(mate_canvas_text_class_init): text-height and
	text-width are not writable. Patch from Olivier Andrieu.
	Closes bug 143499.

2005-05-19  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-pixbuf.c:
	(mate_canvas_pixbuf_render): Use HYPER for interpolation
	instead of _NEAREST in the gdk-pixbuf related code path.
	Closes bug #129891. Patch from Daniel Llano.

2005-05-19  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-line.c: (mate_canvas_line_update):
	Fix a crasher. Patch from Bob Gibbs. Closes bug #127185

2005-05-19  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c:
	(mate_canvas_shape_class_init), (mate_canvas_shape_get_property):
	Fix bug #126113 - width_units property not readable for shapes.
	Patch from Jean Bréfort.

2005-05-19  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas.c: (mate_canvas_item_dispose),
	(mate_canvas_group_destroy), (mate_canvas_destroy): Disposing
	a canvas group should dispose all of its children. Closes
	bug #90259. Patch from Arjan J. Molenaar.

2005-05-19  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-rich-text.c:
	(mate_canvas_rich_text_class_init),
	(mate_canvas_rich_text_get_bounds): Make
	mate_canvas_item_get_bounds() work with Rich Text
	items. Patch from Jean Bréfort. Closes bug #99954.

2005-05-19  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	reviewed by: Tim Janik 

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-bpath.c:
	(mate_canvas_bpath_class_init), (mate_canvas_bpath_set_property),
	(mate_canvas_bpath_get_property):
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-path-def.c: (path_def_boxed_copy),
	(mate_canvas_path_def_get_type):
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-path-def.h: Fixes for perl bindings
	Closes bug #116734. Patch from Muppet <scott at asofyet org>

2005-05-11  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-path-def.c: Fix typo.

2005-05-11  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas.h: Another typo.

2005-05-10  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@mate.org>

