	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-rect-ellipse.c (mate_canvas_ellipse_update): Ditto
	(mate_canvas_rect_update): Ditto

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c (mate_canvas_shape_get_path_def): Signature
	change, check argument
	(mate_canvas_shape_set_path_def): Ditto

2002-01-14  Lauris Kaplinski  <lauris@ximian.com>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c (mate_canvas_shape_update): Free old SVP-s
	in Gdk mode
	(mate_canvas_shape_point): Just return, if there are no SVP-s,
	flood warnings, if canvas->need_update is set
	(mate_canvas_shape_bounds): Implement

2002-01-14  Jody Goldberg <jody@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c (mate_canvas_shape_set_property) : Here we
	  do need to use gdk_rgb_find_color.

2002-01-13  Jody Goldberg <jody@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-text.c (mate_canvas_text_get_property) : Use
	  gdk_colormap_query_color not gdk_rgb_find_color.
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-line.c (mate_canvas_line_get_property) : ditto.
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c (get_color_value) : ditto.

2002-01-13  Jody Goldberg <jody@mate.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-text.c (mate_canvas_text_get_property) : Do not use
	  g_new to allocate (and leak) the color.
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-line.c (mate_canvas_line_get_property) : ditto.
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c (get_color_value) : ditto.
	(mate_canvas_shape_set_property) : PROP_FILL_COLOR_GDK, colorptr can
	  be NULL.

2002-01-11  Alex Larsson  <alexl@redhat.com>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-text.c (mate_canvas_text_set_property):
	Set the font description from the gtk context.

2002-01-10  Anders Carlsson  <andersca@gnu.org>

	* configure.in: Release 1.109.0

2002-01-09  jacob berkman  <jacob@ximian.com>

	* Makefile.am (SUBDIRS): 
	* configure.in: revert removal of libglade support

2002-01-09  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas.c: (emit_event): Remove some dead code.
	(boolean_handled_accumulator): Stolen from gtk.
	(mate_canvas_item_class_init): Moved down to the bottom of the
	file to avoid having to do so many forward declarations. Also
	changed the "event" signal to use G_SIGNAL_TYPE_STATIC_SCOPE for
	efficiency, and boolean_handled_accumulator for consistency with
	event signals in gtk.

Wed Jan  9 06:02:17 2002  Tim Janik  <timj@gtk.org>

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-line.c: fix PROP_FILL_COLOR, PROP_FILL_STIPPLE,
	PROP_WIDTH_PIXELS and PROP_WIDTH_UNITS properties.
	
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c: fix PROP_FILL_STIPPLE, PROP_OUTLINE_STIPPLE,
	PROP_WIND, PROP_DASH, PROP_WIDTH_PIXELS and PROP_MITERLIMIT properties.
	PROP_WIND: eek this is an uint property eventhough ArtSvpWind is
	an enum, but doesn't seem to be exported to the typessystem.
	at least get the value as uint as well.

	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-shape.c (get_color_value): fix this to use
	the canvas, not the item as widget.
	
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas-text.c: fix PROP_CLIP_WIDTH, PROP_FILL_COLOR and
	PROP_FILL_STIPPLE properties.
	
	* libmatecanvas/mate-canvas.c (mate_canvas_item_get_property): don't cast a
	NULL object into G_OBJECT().

